						</p>
						<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-3">
							{skillGroup.data.map((skill) => (
								<span class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/60 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 cursor-default">
									{skill.title}
